# The actual SQLite file lives at backend/dev.db (see db.ts's DATABASE_URL default), NOT under
# prisma/ — this used to say /prisma/dev.db, which matched nothing and let the real dev.db (with
# real CV/vacancy/analysis content from testing) get committed. If you're reading this after that
# happened again, `git rm --cached dev.db` and rotate/purge any exposed content from git history.
/dev.db
/dev.db-journal
